    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/b44e3fd0a7cdd284900ceb121adbbf02.poster.avif?t=1729853405\" width=626 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/b44e3fd0a7cdd284900ceb121adbbf02.webm?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/b44e3fd0a7cdd284900ceb121adbbf02.mp4?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong><br>设计与建造</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造属于自己的音乐节，然后付诸建造，让梦想成真！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Festival Fever》当中，你的目标是举办最盛大、最精彩的音乐节！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从零开始，设计并建造属于你的庆典。搭建舞台、食品摊以及娱乐区，确保符合顾客的需求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搭配阵容<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/cb6568b5a07a83c5cc48789691616165.poster.avif?t=1729853405\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/cb6568b5a07a83c5cc48789691616165.webm?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/cb6568b5a07a83c5cc48789691616165.mp4?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募不同风格的乐队，搭配出超赞的演出阵容。不仅要请来传说级的摇滚巨星，还要帮扶崭露头角的新秀。根据观众喜好，搭配合适的节目，让观众沉浸在整场音乐节中，充满激情地参与每一个环节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/6f40c59a6dd5fc91ea72c8879b818afb.poster.avif?t=1729853405\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/6f40c59a6dd5fc91ea72c8879b818afb.webm?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1849940/extras/6f40c59a6dd5fc91ea72c8879b818afb.mp4?t=1729853405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >举办演出</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好万全准备之后，就可以开始啦。欢迎观众入场，有请第一支乐队上台！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不过，一定要注意音乐节观众的反馈和需求。你需要供应琳琅满目的食物、干净清洁的设施和多种多样的娱乐活动，让观众纷纷打出五星好评。观众玩得开心，音乐节的门票销售额和声誉才能节节攀升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进度与奖励</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若你能够成功举办音乐节，就可以解锁新舞台、新乐队和新的特殊功能。获得奖励和成就，展示你的规划能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >步入《Festival Fever》的世界，建立和管理属于自己的音乐节，体验其中的乐趣。你能否接受挑战，打造一场令人难忘的盛会，成为城里的热门话题？快来试试看吧！</p>",
